Changes made between 1.0 and 1.1

* Connections are now dropped in certain conditions are met:
    - the request has been sent more than 1 minute ago and
    - the connection has an average speed of less than 2 kB/s or the connection
        has been idle for more than 2 minutes.
* Bugfixes

Changes made between 0.9 and 1.0

* Directive `include'
* Subconfigurations
* Fix chroot() and setuid()/setgid()
* Set process title
* Man pages and more documentation
* Better website
* Default thread number to 32
* Better parse error messages
* SIGHUP to reload configuration instead of SIGUSR1
* Various small bug fixes
